    "Tables 10 and 11 list the Friedman test rankings and average rankings of different algorithms on different test sets.",
    "By observing Tables 10 and 11, we can see that the BKA algorithm ranks first in most benchmark functions and first in average rankings.",
    "These statistical data demonstrate the BKA algorithm's excellent performance on a single benchmark function but, more importantly, by evaluating its overall performance, its practicality in multiple optimization problems can be more reliably evaluated.",
